captions.text: Hello, we are Super Junior!
Hi, this is Leeteuk of Super Junior
And this is Eunhyuk
Wait a minute, who are you guys?
Ah.. Siwon?
Oh, Donghae..
The reason why we are here is you know,
We are here to hold the event today
We made a promise when we were starting 'MAMACITA' promotion
that we will present surprise gift for every 1M increase in MAMACITA MV view until it reaches 10M
as Super Junior - we never fail to keep our words
So today we are here to have 'High-five event' with you
We are coming down now to meet you all!
Hello, we are Super Junior!!!
We promised surprise event to you with MAMACITA MV
So we are holding 'High-five' event today
I truly thank you all for your unchanging love for last 10 years
and I'm happy it's not that cold outside thus we could meet tonight
Always love you. Thank you.
Thank you all for coming tonight
Let's feel each other's warmth
Let's have heartwarming time together
